{"tid":1942781,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"豐川市長後悔捐口罩　無錫回贈5萬個 豐川市負責人稱未收到中方聯絡","createTime":"2020-03-25T09:14:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-25T09:20:30.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"58e675abee65a2e3b176bf61f63f8dd34b24baac","tid":1942781,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T09:14:55.000Z","msg":"日本愛知縣豐川市2月初在新冠肺炎疫情於中國肆虐時，向姊妹城市江蘇無錫市新吳區捐贈4500個口罩和防護衣等救援物資。因應疫情在日本爆發，豐川市長竹本幸夫周二（24日）表示後悔當日決定「太天真」，冀中方能歸還庫存口罩。中國駐日大使館周三（25日）宣布，新吳區將回贈豐川市5萬個口罩。<br />\n<br />\n竹本幸夫接受日本東海電視台訪問時，指正與新吳區協商歸還剩餘口罩，說：「如果（新吳區）有庫存的話，能不能還給我們。」他更指自己此刻後悔是馬後炮；據悉愛知縣的庫存口罩將於5月見底。<br />\n<br />\n中國駐日大使館則在Twitter表示，新吳區將陸續向豐川市寄送口罩，第一批已於周二寄出，形容這是中日友好的潛力。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">豐川市負責人周三稱未收到中方聯絡，若屬實會感謝中方。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n受疫情擴散影響，日本政府與國際奧委會周二同意，原定今年7月舉行的東京奧運押後一年。日揆安倍晉三周三與美國總統特朗普通電話約40分鐘，兩人同意日美繼續緊密合作應對疫情，特朗普讚揚延期的決定明智，強調100%支持安倍的建議。<br />\n<br />\n日本截至周三上午11時半，不計疫輪鑽石公主號在內，全國累計超過1214人染疫，43死。當中東京都有171人確診，其次為北海道及愛知縣，愛知縣的死亡人數達17人，為全日本47個都道府縣之冠。另外，長崎縣及山梨縣均人海外返國人士染疫，前者為一名20多歲、英國留學回國的男學生，目前高燒不退；後者為一對30多歲輕症夫婦。"},{"pid":"fd650789832efd8d4c01e8f1426fb6d20266057a","tid":1942781,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T09:16:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"669b593f53805d79065cec430612df82466d82a7","tid":1942781,"uid":160506,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T09:17:31.000Z","msg":"比人當狗咁撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3ac4e60a7ae2ea446608362c79f226a7b67a6d7","tid":1942781,"uid":56999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T09:18:54.000Z","msg":"反正都係得個講字<br />\n<br />\n不如講夠5億個"},{"pid":"50b8bf27429d1e19ac10d1e3497fa27b35f598d7","tid":1942781,"uid":343754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T09:19:31.000Z","msg":"都係果句<br />\n我憑本事借點解要還<br />\n屌你老母<br />\n🖕🏻"},{"pid":"34f4660cef0436dfa4814ab1604becca7d94886c","tid":1942781,"uid":74171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T09:19:37.000Z","msg":"收到先講啦，都唔知係咪性感口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da93a144d16394630badbc4d254f71601edef2f4","tid":1942781,"uid":159870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T09:19:37.000Z","msg":"捐完後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40b59606a7ba0c3935488f5d970b1e5a6d8ef11c","tid":1942781,"uid":239469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T09:19:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd96b0c342fb85d9ef859dbc128b9af3d2b927a0","tid":1942781,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"50b8bf27429d1e19ac10d1e3497fa27b35f598d7","tid":1942781,"uid":343754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T09:19:31.000Z","msg":"都係果句<br />\n我憑本事借點解要還<br />\n屌你老母<br />\n🖕🏻"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T09:20:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}